string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid surprised after seeing its shadow\r\non a pillar and froze in terror.\r\nSkittish Wondroids should avoid pillars...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid slipped after stepping in a puddle,
causing catastrophic damage to cranial chassis.
Wondroids with poor balance should avoid such
obstacles...

string.name: desc
string.value: Trauma from viewing the image of a\r\ndissected android resulted in system crash.\r\nWondroids with low bravery parameters at risk.

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid entangled in conveyor belt,\r\nresulting in immobilization. Plan route with\r\nwardrobe in mind...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid accidentally pressed button
causing nearby machines to malfunction,
resulting in critical damage. Wondroids that
are clumsy and slow must be especially
careful...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid blinded by the bright light
outside and experienced system crash. Overly
sensitive Wondroids must be given time to
adjust to surroundings...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid stubbed toe on threshold causing
pain sensors to overload and resulting in
system crash. Hyperactive Wondroids must be
especially careful!

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid slipped upon landing resulting
in fracture of cranial chassis. Ouch...
Wondroids with poor coordination require
special care...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Sonic frequency resulted in harmonic
resonance damaging poorly shielded sensors
and causing system crash. Hyper-sensitive
Wondroids appear especially susceptible to
sounds.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced overload of emotional
processors resulting in incessant crying.
Caused by exposure to soothing music.
Emotional Wondroids should not listen to
such music...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Exposure to music resulted in Wondroid
getting stuck in endless dance command
loop, and its subsequent capture by
security guard. Wondroids with cheerful
disposition especially at risk...

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid experienced system crash upon\r\nwitnessing the dismantling of other androids.\r\nKeep timid Wondroids away from such sights...

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid immobilized after contact with\r\nharmful substance. Keep an eye on\r\ninattentive Wondroids...

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid immobilized by fear in reaction\r\nto dark environment. Take note when working\r\nwith skittish Wondroids...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid suffered critical damage after
bumping head on object in the dark.
Wondroids that do not mind their surroundings
must be especially cautious...

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid startled by loud machine noises\r\nand became immobilized. Take note when\r\nworking with skittish Wondroids...

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid short-circuited by contact with\r\nelectrified component. Operator should\r\npay more attention when directing Wondroid.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced critical system failure
when hot steam from pipe liquified
sensitive components. Be sure to check for
danger overhead and not to move too quickly.

string.name: desc
string.value: Wondroid immobilized by fear of being\r\ndiscovered by a guard. Be wary with\r\nWondroids prone to overthinking...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced full systems shutdown
upon witnessing interrogation of fellow
Wondroid due to pre-existing trauma. Keep
Wondroids with high empathy quotients away
from such sights.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid lost its footing due to
inattentiveness. Wondroids that are
overeager and don't mind their surroundings
require special supervision...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid attempted to charge its already
full battery, resulting in overheating
and subsequent shutdown. Take care to
prevent over-charging...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid attempted to recharge by connecting
to the wrong electrode resulting in
crippling power surge. Wondroids with
difficult personalities exhibit difficulties
following instructions.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced critical power loss due
to low battery. Wondroids with poor
physical aptitudes and personality problems
seem especially vulnerable to power level
drops...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid's synthetic stomach exploded due to
excessive consumption of human food.
Result: Fatal exception in motor network
Wondroids with greedy personalities appear
especially at-risk.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid detected by Security guard and
subsequently captured. Wondroids with high
physical aptitudes seem especially bad at
stealth...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced systems crash 
resulting from excessive light stimuli to ocular
modules. Clever Wondroids appear especially
susceptible to light...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced critical systems
failure after sitting in chair intended for
Wondroid disassembly. Note: Do not allow
Wondroids to sit in death-chair.

string.name: title
string.value: What Do You Want from Me?

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid experienced systems crash due to
stress resulting from excessive rate of
commands sent by operator. Take care not to
overwhelm stubborn Wondroids with commands.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid immobilized due to system
overheating resulting from receiving
commands it could not carry out. Pay better
attention to Wondroid capabilities in
current scenario...

string.name: desc
string.value:
Overload of Wondroid pain sensors resulting
from damage to fingers sustained while
opening box lid.
Assessment: Wondroid overzealous.

string.name: desc
string.value:
Wondroid overloaded by excessive aural
stimuli when alarm was triggered while
opening box. Appears fatal to all
Wondroids without high
bravery parameters...
